## âš™ï¸ Configuration

### Environment Setup

**Required Environment Variables:**
```bash
# Copy example configuration
cp basil-search/.env.example basil-search/.env

# Edit with your settings
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Optional: For internal site authentication
BASIL_AUTH_TOKEN=your_bearer_token
BASIL_AUTH_HEADER="Basic dXNlcjpwYXNz"
BASIL_CUSTOM_HEADERS='{"X-API-Key":"key","Custom-Header":"value"}'
```

### Service Configuration

| Variable | Service | Description | Required |
|----------|---------|-------------|----------|
| `GROQ_API_KEY` | Search | AI processing API key | âœ… |
| `BASIL_AUTH_TOKEN` | Internal Sites | Bearer token for authenticated sites | âŒ |
| `BASIL_AUTH_HEADER` | Internal Sites | Custom authorization header | âŒ |
| `BASIL_CUSTOM_HEADERS` | Internal Sites | JSON object with custom headers | âŒ |
